This contains code for building a custom select box


Important Points:

1) The select box should be wrapped in a parent div (.select-box-container) with a fixed width
2) This parent div should be relatively positioned in order to position the arrow inside the
   select element (.select-box)
3) To change the size of the selected item, apply the font-size property to the select element 
   (.select-box)
4) To change the size of the menu items, apply the font size property to the option element